Note on Dataset:
This repository includes sample images derived from the "Cards Image
Dataset-Classification" available on Kaggle (by gpiosenka). The dataset is
used here strictly for educational and research purposes as part of a
self-supervised learning demonstration. All rights to the original dataset
remain with its respective creator/publisher. Please refer to the original
Kaggle dataset page for its specific usage terms before redistributing the
image data separately from this project's code.
